# ── Wave 12: 4-signal weight sweep (100 bots, $200 each) ─────────────────────
# Tests all combinations of weights for: price, market_consensus, orderbook_imbalance, funding
# Live formula as of 2026-04-02: 0.70·price + 0.20·mkt + 0.07·imbalance + 0.03·funding
# Key question: what is the optimal weight for each signal?
